flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic data refresh from SAP S/4HANA and external market data sources.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Extract commodity spend and supplier performance data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Perform predictive analytics to forecast supply risks.]
  N2 --> N3[PB: Report Data - Generate market intelligence reports.]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: AutoML - Analyze historical spend data to identify cost-saving opportunities.]
  N4 --> N5{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Present AI recommendations for spend optimization and risk mitigation.}
  N5 -->|Primary| N6[PB: Remote Functions - Execute approved actions and update SAP S/4HANA with new procurement decisions.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital, minimized supply risk, and improved EBITDA through optimized procurement decisions.]
  N5 -->|High supply risk detected| B1[Trigger predefined mitigation actions.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Mitigate supply risk exposure.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Significant cost-saving opportunity i...| B2[Recommend strategic sourcing actions.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Reduce procurement costs.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Market intelligence report ready| B3[Distribute report to key stakeholders.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Influence sourcing and risk strategies.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]